      <h2 class="block-title"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Kami menyediakan alat yang tepat untuk membantu Anda berinteraksi dengan percaya diri di dunia nyata.</font></font></h2>
    

      <div class="homepage-courses-wrapper"><section id="block-homepageskills" class="block block-fixed-block-content block-fixed-block-contenthomepage-skills clearfix">
  
    

      
<div class="wrapper-image">
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field--item">    <img loading="eager" srcset="/sites/podcasts/files/styles/mobile_340_225/public/2023-04/RS9171_GettyImages-1391836113_1440x960_0.jpg?itok=8WQcv8h2 340w, /sites/podcasts/files/styles/630x680/public/2023-04/RS9171_GettyImages-1391836113_1440x960_0.jpg?itok=5DFIIUea 630w" sizes="(max-width:600px) 100px, 100vw." width="340" height="225" src="/sites/podcasts/files/styles/mobile_340_225/public/2023-04/RS9171_GettyImages-1391836113_1440x960_0.jpg?itok=8WQcv8h2" alt="Keterampilan" class="img-responsive">


</div>
      
  </div>
<div class="wrapper-content">
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-title field--type-string field--label-hidden field--item"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Keterampilan</font></font></div>
      
            <div class="field field--name-field-content field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--item"><p><font style="vertical-align: inherit;"><font style="vertical-align: inherit;">Latihlah kemampuan mendengarkan, membaca, menulis, dan berbicara serta pelajari bahasa yang berguna untuk digunakan di tempat kerja atau untuk berkomunikasi secara efektif dengan teman-teman.</font></font></p>

<ul>
